</td>
<td><a href="/thekolwiki/index.php/File:Shadowaccordionthieff.gif" class="image"><img alt="Shadowaccordionthieff.gif" src="http://cdn.coldfront.net/thekolwiki/images/a/a3/Shadowaccordionthieff.gif" width="60" height="100" /></a><br />Female Accordion Thief
</td>
